          <li><a href="/us-20180130102-reliable-rating-system-and-method-thereof/">Wireless</a> networking: Access Points, Wireless Controllers, and Data and Control Planes.</li>
          <li>Networking principles, software, and hardware architectures, ASIC, firmware, high-speed backplanes, switch fabric, control planes, data planes, blocking and non-blocking architectures, priority queuing, time-to-live, packet addressing, and routing/switching table structures.</li>
