          <li>IPv4, IPv6, LAN, WAN, VPN, tunneling, routing protocols, RIP, BGP, MPLS, OSPF, multicast, DNS, QoS, switching, packet switching, layer-2 switching, layer-3 switching, layer-4 switching, application switching, load balancing, and firewalls.</li>
